'''天主教蒙特利瓦諾教區'''（{{lang-la|Dioecesis Monslibanensis}}；{{lang-es|Diócesis de Montelíbano}}）是[[哥倫比亞|哥倫比亞]]一個[[羅馬天主教|羅馬天主教]][[教區|教區]]，屬[[天主教卡塔赫納總教區|卡塔赫納總教區]]。

==歷史==
'''錫努宗座監牧區'''於1924年6月12日成立<ref>{{cite book |title=ACTA APOSTOLICAE SEDIS |volume=XVII |year=1925 |publisher=Typis Polyglottis Vaticanis |pages=5-7 |url=https://www.vatican.va/archive/aas/documents/AAS-17-1925-ocr.pdf |accessdate=2020-03-04 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200304190925/https://www.vatican.va/archive/aas/documents/AAS-17-1925-ocr.pdf |archivedate=2020-03-04 |language=la |dead-url=no }}</ref>，1931年1月12日易名為'''聖-{zh-hans:乔; zh-hk:喬;}-治宗座監牧區'''<ref>{{cite book |title=ACTA APOSTOLICAE SEDIS |volume=XXIV |year=1932 |publisher=Typis Polyglottis Vaticanis |page=39 |url=https://www.vatican.va/archive/aas/documents/AAS-24-1932-ocr.pdf |accessdate=2020-03-04 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200304191338/https://www.vatican.va/archive/aas/documents/AAS-24-1932-ocr.pdf |archivedate=2020-03-04 |language=la |dead-url=no }}</ref>，1950年3月10日升為'''聖-{zh-hans:乔; zh-hk:喬;}-治宗座代牧區'''<ref>{{cite book |title=ACTA APOSTOLICAE SEDIS |series=II |volume=XVII |year=1950 |publisher=Typis Polyglottis Vaticanis |pages=542-543 |url=https://www.vatican.va/archive/aas/documents/AAS-42-1950-ocr.pdf |accessdate=2020-03-04 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200304194825/https://www.vatican.va/archive/aas/documents/AAS-42-1950-ocr.pdf |archivedate=2020-03-04 |language=la |dead-url=no }}</ref>，1969年4月25日升為'''上錫努自治監督區'''<ref>{{cite book |title=ACTA APOSTOLICAE SEDIS |volume=LXI |year=1969 |publisher=Typis Polyglottis Vaticanis |pages=701-702 |url=https://www.vatican.va/archive/aas/documents/AAS-61-1969-ocr.pdf |accessdate=2020-03-04 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200304195335/https://www.vatican.va/archive/aas/documents/AAS-61-1969-ocr.pdf |archivedate=2020-03-04 |language=la |dead-url=no }}</ref>，1998年12月29日升為教區並易名至今<ref>{{cite web |title=MONSLIBANEN* |url=https://w2.vatican.va/content/john-paul-ii/la/apost_constitutions/documents/hf_jp-ii_apc_19981229_monslibanen.html |publisher=Libreria Editrice Vaticana |accessdate=2020-03-04 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200304201353/https://w2.vatican.va/content/john-paul-ii/la/apost_constitutions/documents/hf_jp-ii_apc_19981229_monslibanen.html |archivedate=2020-03-04 |language=la |date=1998-12-29 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==現況==
教區位於[[科爾多瓦省_(哥倫比亞)|科爾多瓦省]]南部，2004年有教友225,000人（佔轄區總人口92.6%）。教區下轄十六個堂區，有廿六名司鐸。現任教區主教為{{link-de|法爾利·約瓦尼·希爾-貝坦庫爾|Farly Yovany Gil Betancur}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 04.03.2020 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2020/03/04/resign.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2020-03-04 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200304170315/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2020/03/04/resign.html |archivedate=2020-03-04 |language=en |date=2020-03-04 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

